snippet.title: Crying Shark
snippet.description:
Parody edits for Shows, Movies and podcasts. I make fictional edits/fan trailers of existing content(shows, podcasts, movies, news) and transform it completely into something absurd or insane (and often inappropriate) video remixes.  Sources include news, podcasts, movies and TV shows.

I create these my videos through heavy editing, effects work, writing new scripts and hiring voice artists. All of my videos are created by me primarily using the editing programs like Adobe Premiere, Adobe After Effects, Audacity and Photoshop.  I change context, remove backgrounds, overlay visuals, VFX, SFX, music transform video and audio to help create new absurd stories and edits.
